great is a 28-minute animated film released in 1975 , telling a humorous version of the life of &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; kingdom brunel . it was directed by bob godfrey , produced by &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; films and distributed by british lion . great won the academy award for animated short film at the 48th academy awards in march 1976 . great was the first british animated film to win an academy award , and also won the bafta award for best animated film in 1976 .